name: Google-maps

# google-maps

***

[Google Maps Web Services API](https://developers.google.com/maps/documentation/webservices/) wrapper for .NET

### Easily access to -
* Geocoding
* Directions
* Elevation
* Places
* Static maps generator


For more info & code samples - read the [wiki](https://github.com/maximnovak/google-maps/wiki) pages

Available on nuget - [http://nuget.org/packages/GoogleMapsApi/](http://nuget.org/packages/GoogleMapsApi/)

**PM> Install-Package GoogleMapsApi**
